OL,3,CMass graves shed new light on 'dark
OL,4,Cchapter' in city's history
OL,6,FThe findings have provided a window
OL,7,Finto the lives of ordinary 19th-
OL,8,Fcentury Bristolians who found
OL,9,Fthemselves at the workhouse due to
OL,10,Fpoverty and hardship.
OL,12,FWriting about the project, Rosanna
OL,13,FPrice, the Engagement Manager, said
OL,14,Fthe story behind these burials
OL,15,Freflects "a dark chapter in Bristol's
OL,16,Fsocial history".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
