OL,3,CMass graves shed new light on 'dark
OL,4,Cchapter' in city's history
OL,6,F"Through these burials, we gain a rare
OL,7,Finsight into how the poorest
OL,8,FBristolians lived and died, offering a
OL,9,Fstark reminder of the challenges faced
OL,10,Fby many during the 19th century."
OL,12,FRichard Leaman, Diocesan Secretary of
OL,13,Fthe Diocese of Bristol, said: "The
OL,14,Fremoval and reinternment of human
OL,15,Fremains have been carried out in a
OL,16,Freverential and lawful manner, with a
OL,17,Fmarker to bear witness to the new
OL,18,Fgravesite."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
